Insider Activity


Individual




Robert J. Phillippy



Mr. Robert J. Phillippy is Independent Director at ESCO Technologies, Inc., President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Newport Corp. and President at Newport Franklin, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at ESCO Technologies, Inc. and Newport Corp. Mr. Phillippy was previously employed as Vice President-Channel Marketing by Schneider Electric SA and Vice President-Channel Marketing by Square D Co. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Texas and an MBA from Kellogg School of Management.



